b Membership.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/GpTiMJ3aS4M', 1, NULL, NULL, 'Junior Licence Application Received - Under Review', '<p>Dear {Name}</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for submitting your Junior Competition Licence application. Your application is currently under review and your reference number is {member-number}.</p>\r\n<p>We aim to process all applications within 5-7 business days. You will receive an email notification once a decision has been made.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions, our friendly office staff are available 9am to 5pm Monday to Friday on 02 4731 5000.</p>\r\n<p>Kind Regards<br/>\r\nThe Team at Karting NSW</p>', 'Junior Licence Application Update - Denied', '<p>Dear {Name}</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for your interest in obtaining a Junior Competition Licence. Unfortunately, we are unable to approve your application at this time. Your reference number is {member-number}.</p>\r\n<p>Reason for decision: {denial-reason}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you believe this decision has been made in error or you would like to discuss your options, please contact our office. In some cases, additional documentation or information may allow us to reconsider your application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions, our friendly office staff are available 9am to 5pm Monday to Friday on 02 4731 5000.</p>\r\n<p>Kind Regards<br/>\r\nThe Team at Karting NSW</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
