<li>Plus have a current Club Membership.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/GpTiMJ3aS4M', 1, NULL, NULL, 'Senior Licence Application Received - Under Review', '<p>Dear {Name}</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for submitting your Senior Competition Licence application. Your application is currently under review and your reference number is {member-number}.</p>\r\n<p>We aim to process all applications within 5-7 business days. You will receive an email notification once a decision has been made.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions, our friendly office staff are available 9am to 5pm Monday to Friday on 02 4731 5000.</p>\r\n<p>Kind Regards<br/>\r\nThe Team at Karting NSW</p>', 'Senior Licence Application Update - Denied', '<p>Dear {Name}</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for your interest in obtaining a Senior Competition Licence. Unfortunately, we are unable to approve your application at this time. Your reference number is {member-number}.</p>\r\n<p>Reason for decision: {denial-reason}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you believe this decision has been made in error or you would like to discuss your options, please contact our office. In some cases, additional documentation or information may allow us to reconsider your application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions, our friendly office staff are available 9am to 5pm Monday to Friday on 02 4731 5000.</p>\r\n<p>Kind Regards<br/>\r\nThe Team at Karting NSW</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(5, 5, 'Event Licence Success - You can now enter for a single Event!', '<p>Dear {Name}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Congratulations on obtaining an Event Licence. Your Sterling Infotech licence number is&nbsp;<strong>{member-number}</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is important for all Event Licence holders to become familiar with the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/rules-regulations/\" target=\"_blank\">Sterling Infotech Rules,</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/technical-specifications/\" target=\"_blank\">Technical Specifications</a>, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/forms-policies/\">Policies</a>&nbsp;on the Sterling Infotech website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions your club cannot assist with, our friendly office staff are available 9am to 5pm Monday to Friday on 02 4731 5000.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kind Regards<br />\r\nThe Team at Sterling Infotech</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/KNSW-Circle-Logo_100px.png\" /></div>', 250, 2, 7, 1000, '<p>Licence off-line&nbsp;</p>', 0, 1, '<p>Allows new or existing competitors aged 7yo and up&nbsp;who wish to enter one (1) upcoming Competition Event/Meeting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To apply for this licence you will need to complete your:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Proof of Identity. For example: Birth Certificate, Passport, Drivers Licence and/or other Government issued Photo ID.</li>\r\n	<li>Profile Picture clearly showing your face.</li>\r\n	<li>Medical Declaration.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/GpTiMJ3aS4M', 1, NULL, NULL, 'Event Licence Application Received - Under Review', '<p>Dear {Name}</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for submitting your Event Competition Licence application. Your application is currently under review and your reference number is {member-number}.</p>\r\n<p>We aim to process all applications within 5-7 business days. You will receive an email notification once a decision has been made.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions, our friendly office staff are available 9am to 5pm Monday to Friday on 02 4731 5000.</p>\r\n<p>Kind Regards<br/>\r\nThe Team at Karting NSW</p>', 'Event Licence Application Update - Denied', '<p>Dear {Name}</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for your interest in obtaining a Event Competition Licence. Unfortunately, we are unable to approve your application at this time. Your reference number is {member-number}.</p>\r\n<p>Reason for decision: {denial-reason}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you believe this decision has been made in error or you would like to discuss your options, please contact our office. In some cases, additional documentation or information may allow us to reconsider your application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions, our friendly office staff are available 9am to 5pm Monday to Friday on 02 4731 5000.</p>\r\n<p>Kind Regards<br/>\r\nThe Team at Karting NSW</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(6, 6, 'You\'re ready to hit the track!', '<p>Dear {Name}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Member ID:&nbsp;[licence-number]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We strongly recommend you speak with your club or a legitimate&nbsp;kart shop before purchasing a go kart, protective equipment or transponder.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is important for all Practice Licence holders to become familiar with the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/rules-regulations/\" target=\"_blank\">Sterling Infotech Rules,</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/technical-specifications/\" target=\"_blank\">Technical Specifications</a>, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/forms-policies/\">Policies</a>&nbsp;on the Sterling Infotech website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions your club cannot assist with, our friendly office staff are available 9am to 5pm Monday to Friday on 02 4731 5000.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kind Regards<br />\r\nThe Team at Sterling Infotech</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/KNSW-Circle-Logo_100px.png\" /></div>', 120, 2, 6, 1000, '', 1, 1, '<p>Allows drivers 6&nbsp;years old&nbsp;and up to&nbsp;practice at Sterling Infotech affiliated clubs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To apply for this licence&nbsp;you will need to complete your:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Proof of Identity. For example:&nbsp;Birth Certificate, Passport, Drivers Licence and/or other Government issued Photo ID.</li>\r\n	<li>Profile Picture clearly showing your face.</li>\r\n	<li>Medical Declaration.</li>\r\n	<li>Plus have a current Club Membership.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/3cYBfuphkuE?rel=0', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(7, 7, 'You\'re all set! Vintage Licence Success', '<p>Dear {Name}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Congratulations on obtaining a Vintage Go Kart Licence. Your Sterling Infotech licence number is&nbsp;<strong>{member-number}.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We strongly recommend you speak with the <a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/vintage-historic-karts-australia/\" target=\"_blank\">Vintage and Historic Kart Club</a> before purchasing a go kart, protective equipment or transponder.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is important for all Competition Licence holders to become familiar with the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/rules-regulations/\" target=\"_blank\">Sterling Infotech Rules,</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/technical-specifications/\" target=\"_blank\">Technical Specifications</a>, and <a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/forms-policies/\">Policies</a> on the Sterling Infotech website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions your club cannot assist with, our friendly office staff are available 9am to 5pm Monday to Friday on 02 4731 5000.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kind Regards<br />\r\nThe Team at Sterling Infotech</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/KNSW-Circle-Logo_100px.png\" /></div>', 80, 2, 15, 1000, '', 1, 1, '<p>For applicants who only wish to participate in Vintage Karting Events/Meetings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To apply for this licence&nbsp;you will need to complete your:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Proof of Identity. For example:&nbsp;Birth Certificate, Passport, Drivers Licence and/or other Government issued Photo ID.</li>\r\n	<li>Profile Picture clearly showing your face.</li>\r\n	<li>Medical Declaration.</li>\r\n	<li>Plus have a current Club Membership.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/MOF_kmsvqvk', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(8, 8, 'You\'re all set! Legal Guardian Licence Success', '<p>Dear {Name}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Member ID:&nbsp;<strong>{member-number}</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you for applying for a Sterling Infotech Legal Guardian Licence.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is important for all Legal Guardian Licences holders to become familiar with the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/rules-regulations/\" target=\"_blank\">Sterling Infotech Rules,</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/technical-specifications/\" target=\"_blank\">Technical Specifications</a>, and <a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/forms-policies/\">Policies</a> on the Sterling Infotech website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note</strong>: You are unable to drive a kart using a Legal Guardian Licence regardless of the circumstances.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions your club cannot assist with, our friendly office staff are available 9am to 5pm Monday to Friday on 02 4731 5000.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kind Regards<br />\r\nThe Team at Sterling Infotech</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/KNSW-Circle-Logo_100px.png\" /></div>', 0, 2, 18, 1000, '', 1, 1, '<p>For any parents and/or Legal Guardians who do not hold a current Drivers Licence.<br />\r\nThis Licence is required to enable parents and/or Legal Guardians to enter a Driver who is under the age of eighteen (18) years into a Competition/Meeting and to manage their Licence status.<br />\r\nThis Licence is required for parents and/or Legal Guardians to access the Race Track, in-grid, out-grid, scrutineering and Parc Ferme restricted areas during a Meeting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note:&nbsp;</strong>You are unable to drive a kart using a Legal / Guardian Licence&nbsp;regardless of the circumstances. This licence has no grading.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To apply for this licence&nbsp;you will need to complete your:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Proof of Identity. For example:&nbsp;Birth Certificate, Passport, Drivers Licence and/or other Government issued Photo ID.</li>\r\n	<li>Profile Picture clearly showing your face.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>A Working With Children&#39;s Check (WWCC) is <strong>not </strong>required for a Legal Guardian&#39;s Licence.</p>', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/_MZzckODIsY?rel=0', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(9, 9, 'You\'re all Set! Pit Crew Licence Application Success', '<p>Dear {Name}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Member ID:&nbsp;{member-number}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you for applying for a Sterling Infotech&nbsp;Pit Crew Licence.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is important for all Pit Crew Licence holders to become familiar with the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/rules-regulations/\" target=\"_blank\">Sterling Infotech Rules,</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/technical-specifications/\" target=\"_blank\">Technical Specifications</a>, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/forms-policies/\">Policies</a>&nbsp;on the Sterling Infotech website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Note: <strong>You are unable to drive a kart using a Pit Crew Licence&nbsp;regardless of the circumstances.&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions your club cannot assist with, our friendly office staff are available 9am to 5pm Monday to Friday on 02 4731 5000.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kind Regards<br />\r\nThe Team at Sterling Infotech</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/KNSW-Circle-Logo_100px.png\" /></div>', 0, 2, 16, 1000, '<p>Licence off-line.</p>', 1, 1, '<p>For any Pit Crew who do not hold a current Drivers or Legal Guardian Licence.<br />\r\nThis Licence is required for mechanics, pit crew, or coaches, who require access to the Race Track, in-grid, out-grid, scrutineering and Parc Ferme restricted areas during a Meeting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note:&nbsp;</strong>You are unable to drive a kart using a Pit Crew Licence&nbsp;regardless of the circumstances. This licence has no grading.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To apply for this licence&nbsp;you will need to complete your:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Proof of Identity. For example:&nbsp;Birth Certificate, Passport, Drivers Licence and/or other Government issued Photo ID.</li>\r\n	<li>Profile Picture clearly showing your face.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/3cYBfuphkuE?rel=0', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(10, 10, 'Lights, Camera, Action!', '<p>Dear {Name}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Member ID:&nbsp;{member-number}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you for applying for a Sterling Infotech&nbsp;Authorised Photographers Licence. Please note, you are <strong>unable </strong>to drive a kart using an Authorised Photographers Licence&nbsp;regardless of the circumstances.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>IMPORTANT:</strong> Please visit the <a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/forms-policies/\">Sterling Infotech website</a> and complete the <em>Authorised Photographers&nbsp;Application Form</em>. This is an important legal document that needs your signature before we can accept your application and issue you with a photographers vest.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We urge you to familiarise yourself with the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/rules-regulations/\" target=\"_blank\">Sterling Infotech Rules</a>&nbsp;and <a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/forms-policies/\">Policies</a> on the Sterling Infotech website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whilst Sterling Infotech do not charge a fee for Authorised Photographers, we ask that 5-10 photos are sent to <a href=\"mailto:info@sterlinginfotech.com?subject=Photos%20for%20promotional%20purposes&amp;body=Hi%2C%0APlease%20find%20attached%20photos%20from%20%3Cevent%3E%20taken%20%3Cdd%2Fmm%2Fyyyy%3E\">info@sterlinginfotech.com</a>&nbsp;for promotional purposes following each event.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions your club cannot assist with, our friendly office staff are available 9am to 5pm Monday to Friday on 02 4731 5000.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kind Regards<br />\r\nThe Team at Sterling Infotech</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/KNSW-Circle-Logo_100px.png\" /></div>', 0, 2, 18, 1000, '<p>Under Maintainance</p>', 1, 1, '<p>For applicants who only wish to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>enter the Race Track area for photography or videography, and/or&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>operate Drones or other Remotely Piloted Aircraft (RPA), and/or&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>sell photos or videos they have captured at Sterling Infotech sanctioned events.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note:&nbsp;</strong>You are unable to drive a kart using this type of licence. This licence has no grading.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To apply for this licence&nbsp;you will need to complete your:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Proof of Identity. For example:&nbsp;Birth Certificate, Passport, Drivers Licence and/or other Government issued Photo ID.</li>\r\n	<li>Profile Picture clearly showing your face.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Working With Children (WWC) check.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/3cYBfuphkuE?rel=0', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(11, 11, 'Thank you for volunteering!', '<p>Dear {Name}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Member ID: <strong>{member-number}</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you for applying for a Sterling Infotech Clerk of Course Licence.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is important for all Officials become familiar with the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/rules-regulations/\" target=\"_blank\">Sterling Infotech Rules,</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/technical-specifications/\" target=\"_blank\">Technical Specifications</a>, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/forms-policies/\">Policies</a>&nbsp;on the Sterling Infotech website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please Note:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>You are&nbsp;<strong>unable&nbsp;</strong>to drive a kart using a&nbsp;Clerk of Course&nbsp;Licence regardless of the circumstances.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>For your&nbsp;Clerk of Course&nbsp;Licence to be valid, you must have a current&nbsp;<strong>Working With Children&#39;s</strong>&nbsp;check, AND you need to have completed&nbsp;<strong>Officials&nbsp;</strong><strong>Training within the last 2 years</strong>.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>We encourage all Officials to visit the Officials HQ website at&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/\">https://sterlinginfotech.com/</a>. Here you will find:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Online Training Courses</li>\r\n	<li>Some helpful Questions &amp; Answers</li>\r\n	<li>As well as the&nbsp;Uniform Policy and the&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/shop/\">Uniform Shop</a>.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions your club cannot assist with, our friendly office staff are available 9am to 5pm Monday to Friday on 02 4731 5000.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kind Regards<br />\r\nThe Team at Sterling Infotech</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/KNSW-Circle-Logo_100px.png\" /></div>', 0, 2, 16, 1000, '', 1, 2, '<p>To apply for this licence you will need to complete your:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Proof of Identity. For example:&nbsp;Birth Certificate, Passport, Drivers Licence and/or other Government issued Photo ID.</li>\r\n	<li>Profile Picture clearly showing your face.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Working With Children (WWC) check.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/3cYBfuphkuE?rel=0', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Your account is suspended', '<p>Dear {Name}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Member ID: <strong>{member-number}</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Your account is suspended.</strong></p>', NULL, NULL),
(12, 12, 'Thank you for volunteering!', '<p>Dear {Name}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Member ID:&nbsp;{member-number}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you for applying for a Sterling Infotech Scrutineers&nbsp;Licence.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is important for all Officials become familiar with the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/rules-regulations/\" target=\"_blank\">Sterling Infotech Rules,</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/technical-specifications/\" target=\"_blank\">Technical Specifications</a>, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/forms-policies/\">Policies</a>&nbsp;on the Sterling Infotech website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please Note:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>You are&nbsp;<strong>unable&nbsp;</strong>to drive a kart using a Scrutineers&nbsp;Licence regardless of the circumstances.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>For your&nbsp;Scrutineers Licence to be valid, you must have a current&nbsp;<strong>Working With Children&#39;s</strong>&nbsp;check, AND you need to have completed&nbsp;<strong>Officials&nbsp;</strong><strong>Training within the last 2 years</strong>.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>We encourage all Officials to visit the Officials HQ website at&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/\">https://sterlinginfotech.com/</a>. Here you will find:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Online Training Courses</li>\r\n	<li>Some helpful Questions &amp; Answers</li>\r\n	<li>As well as the&nbsp;Uniform Policy and the&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/shop/\">Uniform Shop</a>.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions your club cannot assist with, our friendly office staff are available 9am to 5pm Monday to Friday on 02 4731 5000.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kind Regards<br />\r\nThe Team at Sterling Infotech</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/KNSW-Circle-Logo_100px.png\" /></div>', 0, 2, 16, 1000, '', 1, 2, '<p>To apply for this licence you will need to complete your:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Proof of Identity. For example:&nbsp;Birth Certificate, Passport, Drivers Licence and/or other Government issued Photo ID.</li>\r\n	<li>Profile Picture clearly showing your face.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Working With Children (WWC) check.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/3cYBfuphkuE?rel=0', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(13, 13, 'Thank you for volunteering!', '<p>Dear {Name}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Member ID:&nbsp;<strong>{member-number}</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thank you for applying for a Sterling Infotech Stewards Licence.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is important for all Officials become familiar with the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/rules-regulations/\" target=\"_blank\">Sterling Infotech Rules,</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/technical-specifications/\" target=\"_blank\">Technical Specifications</a>, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/forms-policies/\">Policies</a>&nbsp;on the Sterling Infotech website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please Note:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>You are&nbsp;<strong>unable&nbsp;</strong>to drive a kart using a&nbsp;Stewards Licence regardless of the circumstances.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>For your Stewards&nbsp;Licence to be valid, you must have a current&nbsp;<strong>Working With Children&#39;s</strong>&nbsp;check, AND you need to have completed&nbsp;<strong>Officials&nbsp;</strong><strong>Training within the last 2 years</strong>.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>We encourage all Officials to visit the Officials HQ website at&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/\">https://sterlinginfotech.com/</a>. Here you will find:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Online Training Courses</li>\r\n	<li>Some helpful Questions &amp; Answers</li>\r\n	<li>As well as the&nbsp;Uniform Policy and the&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/shop/\">Uniform Shop</a>.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions your club cannot assist with, our friendly office staff are available 9am to 5pm Monday to Friday on 02 4731 5000.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kind Regards<br />\r\nThe Team at Sterling Infotech</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://sterlinginfotech.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/KNSW-Circle-Logo_100px.png\" /></div>', 0, 2, 16, 1000, '', 1, 2, '<p>To apply for this licence you will need to complete your:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Proof of Identity. For example:&nbsp;Birth Certificate, Passport, Drivers Licence and/or other Government issued Photo ID.</li>\r\n	<li>Profile Picture clearly showing your face.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Working With Children (WWC) check.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/3cYBfuphkuE?rel=0', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(20, 20, NULL, NULL, 150, 2, 6, 17, '<p>Under Matainance</p>', 1, 1, '<p>test</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'KartSTART Licence Application Received - Under Review', '<p>Dear {Name}</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for submitting your KartSTART Licence application. Your application is currently under review and your reference number is {member-number}.</p>\r\n<p>We aim to process all applications within 5-7 business days. You will receive an email notification once a decision has been made.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions, our friendly office staff are available 9am to 5pm Monday to Friday on 02 4731 5000.</p>\r\n<p>Kind Regards<br/>\r\nThe Team at Karting NSW</p>', 'KartSTART Licence Application Update - Denied', '<p>Dear {Name}</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for your interest in obtaining a KartSTART Licence. Unfortunately, we are unable to approve your application at this time. Your reference number is {member-number}.</p>\r\n<p>Reason for decision: {denial-reason}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you believe this decision has been made in error or you would like to discuss your options, please contact our office. In some cases, additional documentation or information may allow us to reconsider your application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have any questions, our friendly office staff are available 9am to 5pm Monday to Friday on 02 4731 5000.</p>\r\n<p>Kind Regards<br/>\r\nThe Team at Karting NSW</p>', NULL, NULL, 'test', '<p>tsets testset tes</p>');
